{
  "texts": [
    "Third, propose previously unexplored tasks if they remain relevant.",
    "In addition to guidelines, we should provide examples of output to guide models.Prompt Template 1 (Task Recommendation).- -------------------Initial stage Input: {goal, data} Instruction: You need to come up with a short plan based on the understanding of the data to help accomplish the goal.",
    "Please recommend n exploratory tasks, including task description, type, and data variables.",
    "For task type, you may consider the trend, correlation, category, distribution, etc, to explore the goal from different aspects.",
    "For data variables, list the original column names."
